    <bf:summary>
      <bf:Summary>
	<rdfs:label>PROLA is a complete archive of the American Physical Society's journal publications back to their beginnings in 1893. A subscription to PROLA gives access to all journal content, except for the current year and the preceding three years.</rdfs:label>
      </bf:Summary>
    </bf:summary>
